  "instructions": [
    "Cut the bacon into small pieces and cook in a pan over medium heat until crispy.",
    "Remove the cooked bacon from the pan and set aside.",
    "Add the chopped onion to the pan and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger to the pan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder and garam masala to the pan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the yogurt, cheese, tomato puree, salt, and pepper to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cooked bacon back into the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with naan bread."
